+  /*                                                                       */
+  /*    Normally, you would call this function (followed by a call to      */
+  /*    @FT_Add_Default_Modules or a series of calls to @FT_Add_Module)    */
+  /*    instead of @FT_Init_FreeType to initialize the FreeType library.   */
+  /*                                                                       */
