+   *     Used to indicate application-specific charmaps.
+   *
+   *   TT_PLATFORM_ADOBE ::
+   *     This value isn't part of any font format specification, but is used
+   *     by FreeType to report Adobe-specific charmaps in an @FT_CharMapRec
