+  /*                              glyphs within the font.                  */
+  /*                                                                       */
+  /*    min_Right_Side_Bearing :: The minimum right side bearing of all    */
+  /*                              glyphs within the font.                  */
+  /*                                                                       */
+  /*    xMax_Extent            :: The maximum horizontal extent (i.e., the */
+  /*                              `width' of a glyph's bounding box) for   */
+  /*                              all glyphs in the font.                  */
+  /*                                                                       */
