-   *   FTC_Manager
-   *   FTC_FaceID
-   *   FTC_Face_Requester
-   *
-   *   FTC_Manager_New
-   *   FTC_Manager_Reset
-   *   FTC_Manager_Done
-   *   FTC_Manager_LookupFace
-   *   FTC_Manager_LookupSize
-   *   FTC_Manager_RemoveFaceID
-   *
