-  /*****                                                               *****/
-  /*************************************************************************/
-  /*************************************************************************/
-  /*************************************************************************/
-
-
-  /*************************************************************************
-   *
-   * @type: FTC_FaceID
-   *
-   * @description:
-   *   An opaque pointer type that is used to identity face objects.  The
-   *   contents of such objects is application-dependent.
