-  /*************************************************************************/
-  /*                                                                       */
-  /* <Function>                                                            */
-  /*    FT_Glyph_To_Bitmap                                                 */
-  /*                                                                       */
-  /* <Description>                                                         */
-  /*    Convert a given glyph object to a bitmap glyph object.             */
-  /*                                                                       */
-  /* <InOut>                                                               */
-  /*    the_glyph   :: A pointer to a handle to the target glyph.          */
-  /*                                                                       */
-  /* <Input>                                                               */
-  /*    render_mode :: An enumeration that describes how the data is       */
