-  /*                  (as defined in the OpenType specification; the value */
-  /*                  is the same as the argument to the SCANMODE          */
-  /*                  instruction).                                        */
-  /*                                                                       */
-  /*                  Bits 3 and~4 are reserved for internal purposes.     */
-  /*                                                                       */
