-  /*                  point of each contour within the outline.  For       */
-  /*                  example, the first contour is defined by the points  */
-  /*                  `0' to `contours[0]', the second one is defined by   */
-  /*                  the points `contours[0]+1' to `contours[1]', etc.    */
