-  /* <Description>                                                         */
-  /*    Walk over an outline's structure to decompose it into individual   */
-  /*    segments and Bzier arcs.  This function also emits `move to'      */
-  /*    operations to indicate the start of new contours in the outline.   */
-  /*                                                                       */
